  <h1 class="text-center mb-3">Learn to Drive in Didsbury – MSPSL, Mirror Checks, Test Tips & More</h1>
  <p class="lead text-center">DriveSQ’s DVSA-approved instructors offer focused, structured driving lessons in Didsbury from just <strong>£30/hr</strong>. Whether you're starting fresh or building confidence before your test, we guide you through key routines like MSPSL and mirror checks, and help you master both theory and practical test techniques.</p>

  <h2 class="mt-4">Local Learning for Local Roads</h2>
  <p>Didsbury has the perfect mix of quiet residential streets and complex multi-lane junctions — ideal for building confidence. Our lessons start in quieter areas, helping you understand mirror routines and basic control, before progressing to main roads like Kingsway (A34) and Wilmslow Road, where you’ll learn positioning, planning and lane choice under real conditions.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Pricing in Didsbury:</strong> Just £30/hr</li>
    <li><strong>Nearby Test Centres:</strong> West Didsbury, Sale, Cheetham Hill</li>
    <li><strong>Lesson Options:</strong> Manual & Automatic, Evening/Weekend Slots Available</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="mt-4">MSPSL Routine Explained</h3>
  <p>MSPSL stands for <strong>Mirror, Signal, Position, Speed, Look</strong>. It’s the foundation of safe and defensive driving:</p>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Mirror:</strong> Always check your rearview and side mirrors before changing speed or direction.</li>
    <li><strong>Signal:</strong> Let other road users know what you're doing early enough.</li>
    <li><strong>Position:</strong> Move into the correct road position for your next action.</li>
    <li><strong>Speed:</strong> Adjust speed smoothly, depending on the situation.</li>
    <li><strong>Look:</strong> Check all around before making your move – including blind spots.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>The 6-Point Mirror Check</h3>
  <p>Before moving off, always check:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Left blind spot</li>
    <li>Left mirror</li>
    <li>Rearview mirror</li>
    <li>Right mirror</li>
    <li>Right blind spot</li>
    <li>Front (check road ahead)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Theory & Practical Test Preparation</h3>
  <p>We offer tailored support for your theory test, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Hazard perception techniques</li>
    <li>Understanding road signs & markings</li>
    <li>Mock theory tests with feedback</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Practical test lessons include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Independent driving (sat nav or signs)</li>
    <li>Reversing manoeuvres (bay/parallel/1 in 3 choice)</li>
    <li>Show Me / Tell Me car checks</li>
    <li>Mock practical test routes around Didsbury</li>
  </ul>

